{"tid":1312410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有居民批評待大部分示威者離去後展示警力造成不便","createTime":"2019-07-13T13:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T14:05:10.000Z","uid":212626,"like":90,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"93aa204baaff7fbf5c7f5bab572e811bda4b006f","tid":1312410,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:38:13.000Z","msg":"警方在上水反水貨遊行後清場，警員防線沿行人天橋上推進至上水新都廣場，一度在商場外舉起黃旗，商場保安其後鎖起前往行人天橋的入口，市民要由地面出入口離去。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有市民批評，警方在大部分示威者離去後，才封閉行人天橋及道路，是想展示警力，亦浪費納稅人金錢，對居民造成不便。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468221-20190713.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468221-20190713.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=2075fca3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468221-20190713.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=367e0498\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468221-20190713.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"1c524e1a73f54cdd6257b60022a873ff6366a437","tid":1312410,"uid":11804,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:38:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d66683195199024e72ab23a541a91a476dcf2292","tid":1312410,"uid":51271,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:39:00.000Z","msg":"呃OT唔駛你教"},{"pid":"52d0613e46cd08d25432823399fc704eba5f0be1","tid":1312410,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:39:09.000Z","msg":"根本就係 仲要抄身份證先過得ON9?"},{"pid":"e6357754c665aa9ba9bb8353775d6202b7f16635","tid":1312410,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1c524e1a73f54cdd6257b60022a873ff6366a437","tid":1312410,"uid":11804,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:38:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T